string.text:
The ritual is done. You and your clan now belong to Chaos:
- you may recruit Chaos troops in your fiefs;
- your settlements no longer lose loyalty over a foreign culture;
- the servants of Chaos no longer treat you as an outsider;
- the Gods grant raw martial power (your weapon and athletics skills surge).
To mortal eyes your body is unchanged - the mark of Chaos lies on your soul.
